com.incadencecorp.coalesce.framework.persistance

Interface ICoalescePersistor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AccumuloPersistor, CoalescePersisterWrapper, CoalescePersistorBase, DerbyPersistor, FilePersistorImpl, MockPersister, MockSearchPersister, Neo4JPersistor, Neo4jSearchPersister, PostGreSQLPersistor, PostGreSQLPersistorExt, PostGreSQLPersistorExt2

    public interface ICoalescePersistor
    Interface for storing and retrieving Coalesce entities from different databases depending on the implementation.
